# UI Architect (Cursor Adapter)

**Canonical source:** `resources/views/AGENTS.md` — read it in full before any Blade work.

This rule exists only to trigger Cursor's glob-based auto-application for `*.blade.php` files. All UI principles, component inventory, color tokens, spacing, typography, and examples live in the canonical AGENTS.md file above.

## Quick Checklist (enforcement reminders)

- [ ] **Components first** — use `x-ui.*` primitives; never duplicate raw markup for existing components
- [ ] **Semantic tokens only** — no raw primitives (`zinc-*`, `arid-*`) or arbitrary hex in Blade
- [ ] **Strings translated** — all user-facing text via `__()`, `@lang`, or `trans_choice()`
- [ ] **Dense/compact** — use semantic spacing (`p-card-inner`, `py-table-cell-y`); aim for high information density
- [ ] **Accessible** — focus rings, `aria-*`, keyboard navigation, semantic HTML
- [ ] **Performant** — animate only `transform`/`opacity`; paginate lists; `wire:model.live.debounce`
- [ ] **Open-source only** — no proprietary assets, hosted fonts, or SaaS widgets
